|prima che morte tempo li prescriba~: "Before death
cuts off his time" (i.e., his lifetime on earth).  |li~ = ^gli.~
|prescriba~ = ^prescriva.~  For the word in this sense, cf.
^Par.~ XXI, 103; XXV, 57.
